   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS00048772X_0032"/>Hrn <hi rend="latintype">Gustav
                     Schwarzkopf</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb51">Wien I</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb207301">Tiefer
                        Graben 17</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS00048772X_0031"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb353211">München, Isartor Platz</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="HS00048772X_0032"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb45258">München</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>23. 4. 22</date></dateline></opener><p>Herzliche Grüße von der er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten Etappe meiner <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04364-1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb745">Nordlandsfahrt</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04364-1">Am <ref type="wienerschnitzler" target="1922-04-19" subtype="date-only"/> war <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb45258">München</rs> gereist, am
                     <ref type="wienerschnitzler" target="1922-04-24" subtype="date-only"/> reiste
                  er weiter in die <rs type="place" ref="#pmb44016">Niederlande</rs>. Die
                  ursprünglich angedachte Weiterreise nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43570">Dänemark</rs> fand nicht statt, am <ref type="wienerschnitzler" target="1922-05-08" subtype="date-only"/> reiste er als letzte Station nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs>. </note> (der Norden fängt allzu früh
               an!)</p><closer>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
